value.name: Retsplejeloven § 732

value.name: Area codes 732 and 848 - Wikipedia
value.snippet: Area codes 732 and 848 are telephone area codes in the North American Numbering Plan (NANP) for parts of the U.S. state of New Jersey. History [ edit ] In the original configuration of the first nationwide telephone numbering plan of 1947, all of New Jersey was a single numbering plan area (NPA), assigned the first of all area codes, 201 .
